               <msContents>
                  <summary>Asmat prayer against charm; Asmat prayer for healing; Asmat prayer against charm; Asmat Prayer against Däsk and Gadale and Epilepsy; and other asmat prayers in various hands; Absolution of the Son, Fǝtḥat zä-Wäld. ፍትሐት፡ ዘወልድ፡, Feast days of the twelve Apostles and Evangelists; Prayer against the Tongue of People</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="4v" facs="003"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against charm, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡.</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am">Gǝ‘ǝz and Amharic</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="4v" to="6r" facs="007"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for healing</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ…ፍታህ፡ ቅህዱን፡ እርክያን፡.</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am">Gǝ‘ǝz and Amharic</textLang>
                </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i3"><locus from="6r" to="8v" facs="008"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against charm, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡.</foreign></title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am">Gǝ‘ǝz and Amharic</textLang>
                </msItem>
                <msItem xml:id="ms_i4"><locus from="8v" to="76v" facs="011"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat Prayer against Däsk and Gadale and Epilepsy</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ: አብ: <gap reason="omitted"/> በዝንቱ አስማቲከ: ዘፈታህኮሙ : እማእሰሪሁ: ለሞት: ሥራየ: ደስክ: ወጐዳሌ: ሥራየ: ባሪያ:</incipit>
